\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\rho zn}{q(\theta_{t})}$
\end_inset

.
 If the firm lose 10 workers,
 they want to hire 10 workers to replace them.
 But if the hiring rate,
 
\begin_inset Formula $q(\theta_{t}),$
\end_inset

